transcripts.text: Part of our calling is to fight for the Lord, to fight for our nation, and tremendous battles will be won.  There comes a time when all you can do is make your stand, and if you will, the God, the way maker, he comes through.  Allow this aggressive kind of faith that we're called to, allow it to rise and make a stand.  Fight.  Make a stand.  Fight it.  Don't take it.  Don't be a passive warrior and say, well, it is what it is.  Change it.  Come and let's agree together that our victory is irreversible.
